# Runtime data - listening history, images, the database (Spotify session
# cookies included), and the flask secret key file are personal/sensitive and
# must never be committed. Database/Users/ is the pre-1.7.0 name, kept here too
# since existing local checkouts won't have renamed it until their next start.
